PrecisAmendment to the CANADA OIL AND GAS PRODUCTION AND CONSERVATION REGULATIONS which insert cross-references to the new "Fitness" and "Installations" Regulations and require an operator to obtain a Certificate of Fitness where the work is to be carried out in offshore areas.
